                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1993-18390617 t18390617-1993-punishment-236"></join>Death recorded</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
